11#include "modules/audio_processing/aec3/subtractor_output.h"
12
13#include <numeric>
14
15namespace webrtc {
16
17SubtractorOutput::SubtractorOutput() = default;
18SubtractorOutput::~SubtractorOutput() = default;
19
20void SubtractorOutput::Reset() {
21 s_refined.fill(0.f);
22 s_coarse.fill(0.f);
23 e_refined.fill(0.f);
24 e_coarse.fill(0.f);
25 E_refined.re.fill(0.f);
26 E_refined.im.fill(0.f);
27 E2_refined.fill(0.f);
28 E2_coarse.fill(0.f);
29 e2_refined = 0.f;
30 e2_coarse = 0.f;
31 s2_refined = 0.f;
32 s2_coarse = 0.f;
33 y2 = 0.f;
34}
35
36void SubtractorOutput::ComputeMetrics(rtc::ArrayView<const float> y) {
37 const auto sum_of_squares = [](float a, float b) { return a + b * b; };
38 y2 = std::accumulate(y.begin(), y.end(), 0.f, sum_of_squares);
39 e2_refined =
40 std::accumulate(e_refined.begin(), e_refined.end(), 0.f, sum_of_squares);
41 e2_coarse =
42 std::accumulate(e_coarse.begin(), e_coarse.end(), 0.f, sum_of_squares);
43 s2_refined =
44 std::accumulate(s_refined.begin(), s_refined.end(), 0.f, sum_of_squares);
45 s2_coarse =
46 std::accumulate(s_coarse.begin(), s_coarse.end(), 0.f, sum_of_squares);
47
48 s_refined_max_abs = *std::max_element(s_refined.begin(), s_refined.end());
49 s_refined_max_abs =
50 std::max(s_refined_max_abs,
51 -(*std::min_element(s_refined.begin(), s_refined.end())));
52
53 s_coarse_max_abs = *std::max_element(s_coarse.begin(), s_coarse.end());
54 s_coarse_max_abs = std::max(
55 s_coarse_max_abs, -(*std::min_element(s_coarse.begin(), s_coarse.end())));
56}
57
58} // namespace webrtc
